<li id="cite_note-7"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.google.com/patents?id=pIpDAAAAEBAJ&amp;printsec=abstract&amp;zoom=4&amp;#PPP1,M1" class="external text" title="http://www.google.com/patents?id=pIpDAAAAEBAJ&amp;printsec=abstract&amp;zoom=4&amp;#PPP1,M1" rel="nofollow">Improvement in photographic pictures</a>, Henry Fox Talbot, United States Patent Office, patent no. 5171, June 26 1847.</li>
<li id="cite_note-levenson-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-levenson_8-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFLevenson1993">Levenson, G. I. P (May 1993). "Berkeley, overlooked man of photo science". <i>Photographic Journal</i> <b>133</b> (4): 169–71.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Berkeley%2C+overlooked+man+of+photo+science&amp;rft.jtitle=Photographic+Journal&amp;rft.aulast=Levenson&amp;rft.aufirst=G.+I.+P&amp;rft.au=Levenson%2C+G.+I.+P&amp;rft.date=May+1993&amp;rft.volume=133&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=169%E2%80%9371&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:History_of_photography"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Loke.2C_Margarett_.282000.29.2C_The_New_York_Times.2C_7_July.2C_Arts-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Loke.2C_Margarett_.282000.29.2C_The_New_York_Times.2C_7_July.2C_Arts_9-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0DE5DD1F39F934A35754C0A9669C8B63&amp;sec=&amp;spon=&amp;partner=permalink&amp;exprod=permalink" class="external text" title="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0DE5DD1F39F934A35754C0A9669C8B63&amp;sec=&amp;spon=&amp;partner=permalink&amp;exprod=permalink" rel="nofollow">"PHOTOGRAPHY REVIEW; In a John Brown Portrait, The Essence of a Militant"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0DE5DD1F39F934A35754C0A9669C8B63&amp;sec=&amp;spon=&amp;partner=permalink&amp;exprod=permalink" class="external free" title="http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0DE5DD1F39F934A35754C0A9669C8B63&amp;sec=&amp;spon=&amp;partner=permalink&amp;exprod=permalink" rel="nofollow">http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9E0DE5DD1F39F934A35754C0A9669C8B63&amp;sec=&amp;spon=&amp;partner=permalink&amp;exprod=permalink</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-03-16</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=PHOTOGRAPHY+REVIEW%3B+In+a+John+Brown+Portrait%2C+The+Essence+of+a+Militant&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fquery.nytimes.com%2Fgst%2Ffullpage.html%3Fres%3D9E0DE5DD1F39F934A35754C0A9669C8B63%26sec%3D%26spon%3D%26partner%3Dpermalink%26exprod%3Dpermalink&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:History_of_photography"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
